               <p>OLD COURT.</p>
               <p>SECOND DAY, FRIDAY, FEBRUARY 20.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury. - Before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</p>
               <p>584. 
               
                  <persName id="t18290219-59-defend580" type="defendantName">
                     MARY ANN 
                     SMITH
                  <interp inst="t18290219-59-defend580" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
